<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Gift Card Redemption for <%= studioName %></title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
			}
			.container {
				max-width: 600px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 20px;
				background-color: #f9f9f9;
				border: 1px solid #ddd;
			}
			.header,
			.footer {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			.header img {
				max-width: 100px;
			}
			.content {
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			.redemption-details {
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			.redemption-table {
				width: 100%;
				border-collapse: collapse;
				margin-top: 10px;
			}
			.redemption-table th,
			.redemption-table td {
				border: 1px solid #ddd;
				padding: 8px;
				text-align: left;
			}
			.redemption-table th {
				background-color: #f2f2f2;
			}
			.footer {
				font-size: 12px;
				color: #777;
			}
			.regards {
				margin-top: 20px;
				border-radius: 5px;
				font-style: italic;
			}
			.regards p {
				margin: 0;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="header">
				<img src="<%= logoUrl %>" alt="Logo" />
			</div>

			<div class="content">
				<p>Dear <%= studioName %> Team,</p>
				<h3>Gift Card Redemption Confirmation</h3>
				<p>
					We're pleased to confirm that you have successfully redeemed one of
					your gift cards. Here are the details of your transaction:
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="redemption-details">
				<table class="redemption-table">
					<tr>
						<th>Gift Card Code</th>
						<td><%= giftCardCode %></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>Amount Redeemed</th>
						<td><%= redeemedAmount %></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>Current Balance</th>
						<td><%= availableAmount %></td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</div>

			<div class="content">
				<p>
					Thank you for using our gift card service. If you have any questions
					about this redemption, please don't hesitate to contact our customer
					support team.
				</p>
				<p>
					Remember, you can check all your redeemed gift cards anytime through
					your dashboard at
					<a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>"><%= websiteUrl %></a>.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="regards">
				<p><strong>Best regards,</strong></p>
				<p>Thai-Massage.de Team</p>
			</div>

			<div class="footer">
				<p>
					For support, please contact:
					<a href="mailto:support@thai-massage.de">support@thai-massage.de</a>
				</p>
				<p>
					&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Thai-Massage.de. All rights
					reserved.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
